    "Thus the propagator realities for K e, G e ′ will continue to hold for p ∈ N. To further check the ψ n -reality and k T -reality, we need to examine how the vertex D v transforms under Wick rotation: 22D v = a 4-kv-lv (η) (δ ij) pv (ϵ ijk) qv (∂ η) kv (i k i) lv partially contract = i (-4+kv+lv)p i -kv i lv × a 4-kv-lv (χ) (δ ij) pv (ϵ ijk) qv (∂ χ) kv (k i) lv partially contract = i (kv+lv)(p+1) × real, (D.11)which is real for arbitrary couplings (i.e.",
